Others: Matas Buzelis played 6:24 minutes off the bench for the Chicago Bulls against the Minnesota Timberwolves.
At the time of writing, the Bulls held a slender 45-39 lead over the T-Wolves.
Buzelis recorded no rebounds or assists but had one steal and one block.
He shot 0-1 from the field and 0-1 from beyond the arc.
Nikola Vucevic and Coby White led the side with nine points each.
